  <description>
      <p>Available emulated models are:</p>
      <ul>
          <li>Classic serie (HP 35, HP 80, HP 45, HP 70)</li>
          <li>2nd Generation / Woodstock serie (HP 21, HP 22, HP 25, HP 25c, HP 27, HP 29c, HP 67)</li>
          <li>3rd Generation / Spice serie (HP 31e, HP 32e, HP 33e, HP 33c, HP 34c, HP 37e, HP 38c, HP 38e)</li>
          <li>Voyager serie (HP 10c, HP 11c, HP 12c, HP 15c, HP 16c)</li>
      </ul>
    <p>Right-click on icon to set preferred model, or run <code>flatpak run io.github.mike632t.x11_calc --setup</code></p>
    <p>For optimal rendering, following fonts are recommanded: <code>xfonts-base</code> (Debian/Ubuntu), <code>xorg-x11-fonts-base</code> or <code>xorg-x11-fonts-misc</code> (Fedora), <code>font-misc-misc</code> (Gentoo).</p>
  </description>

